{
  "stem": "1400.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But before I go further, in the liberation day, I saw-- witnessed this, that some of the Nazi guards who were left, because the command-- high command already left the camp early-- some of the Nazi guards hid in the garbage dump, which was a deep-- a tractor was able to go in there and had a cover on it.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Hid in there and when we were liberated, the concentration camp inmates seek them out, started to stone them and beat them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the Seventh Army detail came in and held a gun against us not to beat them to death.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Some of them were already, but we were held at bay not to do that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Went to the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't take it any longer and they grabbed the electrified wire to get out of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About three weeks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have papers as I follow through Prague and Bratislava, Czechoslovakia going toward home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the, the American troop carriers, trucks, they dropped us off in Prague.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went through a disinfection again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they directed us, if you want to go at that time, the trains were going.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it looks like nobody needed tickets because we were traveling on top of the train and on the tail end of the train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was so loaded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went to Bratislava, and I have a piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went through again disinfection in Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is how I arrived on the top of the train to Nove Zamky, to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I spent, in Nove Zamky-- I don't know if a day or two.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was very little organization in this little town.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
